  "passage": [
    "Tia feels a tap in her coat pocket. An egg cracks—tap, tap! A baby dragon hatches. Its wings are soft and its tail curls. |'Hello, Pocket Dragon,' says Tia.",
    "The dragon gives a tiny spark—pop! A warm glow fills Tia’s hands. |'Only gentle sparks,' says Tia. 'We keep things safe.' The dragon nods.",
    "That night the lights go out. Tia picks up a paper lantern. The dragon climbs into the pocket and glows to guide the way down the hall.",
    "They help Gran find her keys under the chair. Neighbours smile. |'Thank you, little guide,' says Gran. Tia pats the gentle dragon’s tail."
  ],
